arStrings.szText:
{c_label}Lucky Hit:{/c} Your {c_important}Marksman{/c} Skills have up to a {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 2"|%|]{/c} chance to create an {c_important}Arrow Storm{/c} at the enemy's location, dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} Physical damage over {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds. 

Your {c_important}Arrow Storms{/c} deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%|]{/c} increased damage.

{c_important}Marksman{/c} Skills can make an {c_important}Arrow Storm{/c}, dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} Physical damage. Your {c_important}Arrow Storms{/c} deal more damage.
